title: Nick Foles future, Free Agency buzz, Super Bowl fallout with Jason La Canfora (Football 2/7)
description:
Will Brinson and CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora break down everything that happened during Super Bowl week (5:00), possible fallout for the Rams after losing to the Patriots (15:00), Greg Schiano to the Pats (27:00), the hiring of Brian Flores and plans for Ryan Tannehill (28:00), what Zac Taylor will do with Andy Dalton (31:00), what will happen with Nick Foles and the Eagles (35:00) and what teams could do in free agent (40:00).
